These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
House: victorian, cottage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat
1. the victorian house is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the victorian house is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
6. the siglo-smoker is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Birthday      | april      | december |
| Food          | orange      | onion       |
| House         | cottage | victorian  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | satire      |
| Pet   | goldfish       | ferret      |
| Cigar         | baccarat    | siglo       |

