2 different games are played: go, bridge
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, trance
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, pink
House: victorian, craftsman
1. the nurse is not to the left of the person playing go##8
2. the teacher is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
3. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the nurse is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| City          | nizza | hamburg |
| Game         | go  | bridge  |
| Job           | nurse      | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | pop      |
| Color           | coral     | pink    |
| House     | victorian  | craftsman     |

